headline: Hyatt Hotels, Marriott Vacations, Travel + Leisure, Xponential Fitness, and Polaris Shares Skyrocket, What You Need To Know
summary: A number of stocks jumped in the afternoon session after the latest Consumer Price Index (CPI) report came in largely as expected, reinforcing investor hopes for an upcoming Federal Reserve interest rate cut.
